Class ReplenishmentRequest

java.lang.Object
ReplenishmentRequest
public class ReplenishmentRequest extends Object
The `ReplenishmentRequest` class represents a request for replenishing the stock of a specific medicine. It contains details such as the request ID, medicine name, requested quantity, pharmacist ID, and status.
